      "source": "Example 2: Connected components (undirected graph)\n\n\n1 -- 2     3 ---- 4------9      11    12 ---- 13  \n| \\  |           /|      | \n|  \\ |          / |      |\n|   \\|         /  |      |\n5    6        7   8 ---- 10  \n",
